pageProduct.name: Wagner Colostrum Milk Powder 250g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

  • Natural colostrum drink
  • Contains IgG immunoglobulins
  • Each great-tasting serve of vanilla-flavoured Wagner Colostrum Milk Powder provides 48mg of IgG immunoglobulins

Features

  • Wagner Colostrum Milk Powder is a delicious powder designed for dispersing into water or milk for a delicious drink.
  • Colostrum is the natural "first food" that cows produce for their new born calves.
  • This food contains no artificial colours,

Warnings

Always read and the label; and take as directed.

Gluten, wheat, egg, soy, artificial colours, artificial sweeteners or artificial flavours.

 

Ingredients

Ingredients
Skim Milk Powder (75%), Lactose, Colostrum Powder (8.8%), Natural Flavours. Contains Milk.

Directions

Adults and children - mix 1 rounded scoop (3g scoop) in milk or water.
